      "lk_opt_5": "Daily",
      "sec_section_a_the_next_five_questions_ask_ab_title": "Section A.The next five questions ask about e-cigarette advertisements. Do not think about cigarettes or other tobacco products when answering these questions.",
      "self_reported_exposure_to_smoking_on_media_ecig_internet": "When you are using the Internet, how often do you see ads or promotions for e-cigarettes?",
